_sText:
Minecraft surf map I made for Anti Gravity surf-server, but everyone is free to use it!

It's a basic combat-surf designed for short rounds and minimum hideouts and camping spots.

Please try out the map before doing any form of commenting and/or rating, thanks


**EDIT** - I failed hard on one thing, cause of the fact that this is my first map in a long time i forgot all about the fact that i needed to pack the texture files within the .bsp file in order for people to see the textures, sorry! Its fixed!
